author: eTN Editor
title: Seychelles Consulate in USA to mark World Affairs Council event
text:
Click here for information and nomination Seychelles Consulate in USA to mark World Affairs Council event 
The Annual State of Washington Consular Association Reception was held in September at the Annie Wright Seminary in Tacoma, Washington, hosted by the World Affairs Council, Tacoma. The Seychelles Honorary Consul, Beth Willis, carried the Seychelles flag at this event which was also an opportunity for the island's representative to network and increase the visibility of the Seychelles. 
Today the mid-ocean islands of the Seychelles is marketed in the USA as an add-on from a Big Five Safari in Africa. The Seychelles Tourism Board launched a couple of years ago the tagline "From the Big Fiveâ€¦to the Best Five" after launching the safari-beach holiday option for Americans. 
Seychelles is a founding member of the International Coalition of Tourism Partners (ICTP) . Oct 23, 2015 Source: Seychelles Ministry of Tourism and Culture
